{"tid":1519153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[香城Online]-地圖更新-城西資料片 ver 8.31","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T04:33:46.000Z","uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93a65376aee9b65926997acfe3a37f1cb1b54bd3","tid":1519153,"uid":289654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x6xmP6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx6xmP6C.jpg&h=d13ffd72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n致各香城Online 玩家<br />\n由於新增地圖關卡存在巨大安全風險<br />\n為保玩家齊上齊落<br />\n在此更新城西資料片 ver 8.31<br />\n<br />\n由於香城鐵路存在極大關站風險<br />\n請各玩家留意進攻撤退路線<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅圈</span>為終極大佬<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍圈</span>為伏兵處所<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">橙色</span>為伏兵過往兵力聚集地方<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span>為進攻撤退路線<br />\n東向西橫向路線，由海邊起<br />\n干諾道中/西<br />\n德輔道中/西，於西港城斷開<br />\n皇后大道中/西<br />\n荷里活道，由東華醫院至中區半山行人電梯<br />\n堅道，般咸道至HKU<br />\n<br />\n南北向連接海邊至半山<br />\n東至西為<br />\n花園道(版面所限，無show)<br />\n半山行人電梯<br />\n上環禧利街<br />\n醫院道<br />\n東邊街<br />\n<br />\n最後，跟據過往兵力集結，<br />\n玩家留<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好搞後面路線</span><br />\n伏兵會好驚架<br />\n另外，跟據地理位置反包圍<br />\n<br />\n另外，由於跟據情報<br />\n伏兵已經改變策略<br />\n小心大街小巷包圍<br />\n留意信息及哨兵<br />\n<br />\n資料片尤如大型城市定向<br />\n請熟讀地圖<br />\n希望玩家可以一齊黎一齊走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166d8a1325bbd07a489e5851acdc904f3c9964d2","tid":1519153,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0gexVh8qxZHo